# Decision Log

Records of significant architectural, library, and design decisions with rationale.

## Convention

Each decision is a separate markdown file named `NNN-short-title.md` (zero-padded to three digits).

## Template

```markdown
# NNN: Decision Title

Date: YYYY-MM-DD
Status: Proposed | Accepted | Superseded by NNN

## Context

What is the issue that motivates this decision?

## Decision

What is the change that we are proposing or have agreed to?

## Consequences

What becomes easier or more difficult because of this decision?
```

